        {"key": "tutorial.step1", "value": "You picked your first venture.\nYour rival starts in the same sector.\nThis 25-turn run is about surviving pressure, building a stronger board,\nand finishing the market fight ahead.\n\nYour goal: end the run with the bigger market share."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step2", "value": "This table has 3 zones.\nBottom: your business board.\nMiddle: district pressure, traffic, ratings, and market pull.\nTop: the rival board and their visible moves."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step3", "value": "Your hand is your decision space.\nEach turn you draw options and spend actions to build, react,\nor pressure the market.\nSome cards stay on the board. Some are short-term responses."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step4", "value": "Setup cards build capacity.\nGrowth cards create demand.\nRisk cards spike power but raise danger.\nReaction cards repair trust, quality, or stability."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step5", "value": "On the left of your board is your venture anchor.\nThis is your storefront or app HQ.\nYour first core operation starts here and upgrades make it grow."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step6", "value": "Watch the main loop:\nMarketing raises demand.\nOperations and staff raise capacity.\nSuppliers improve quality or margin.\nIf demand beats capacity, rating falls and organic traffic slows."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step7", "value": "These action pips show how many moves you still have.\nA strong turn usually mixes growth with stability,\nnot just raw expansion."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step8", "value": "Press END TURN when you're ready.\nThen the rival acts, the market resolves,\nand your cash, rating, and market share update."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step9", "value": "Rival phase: watch which lane they pressure.\nPrice, quality, growth, staffing, or expansion.\nTheir cards are signals you can answer next turn."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step10", "value": "Resolve phase compares demand, capacity, quality,\nrating, upkeep, and risk.\nGood sequencing becomes profit.\nBad sequencing becomes pressure."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step11", "value": "Turn report: check why your money, rating,\nand market share changed.\nIf trust slips or overload hits, the report tells you why."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step12", "value": "Need a different answer? Open SHOP.\nBuy cost gets a card into your economy.\nPlay cost activates it.\nUpkeep and salary are what you carry every turn."},
        {"key": "tutorial.step13", "value": "Tips to dominate:\n\n\u2022 Demand without capacity destroys rating\n\u2022 Supplier and staff quality create organic growth\n\u2022 Risk cards are short-term power, not free value\n\u2022 Watch the rival lane and answer the right pressure"},
        {"key": "tutorial.step14", "value": "Build the board. Protect trust. Scale at the right speed.\nFinish stronger than the rival by turn 25.\n\nGood luck."},
        {"key": "tutorial.begin", "value": "Begin"},
